title: DELIVERED Ending Explained! Into The Dark Hulu
author: Think Story
comment:
Jenny: Would you like to come to my secluded home while you're eight and a half weeks pregnant?
Valerie: Sure!
For once I'd like one of these stories with a pregnant woman in danger who didn't want her child to end with her still not wanting her child. I'd like to see how that plays out.
Based on a true story of a woman this happened to in DC. Her “how I survived story is crazy!”
Big lesson here. Always double tap. If you get a hit in on your attacker hit them again because otherwise they'll most likely get back up and come at you harder.
Chest bursting babies makes me think of the chest burst era from the Alien franchise.
description:
In this video we take a deep dive, review, recap and explain the ending to Hulu's Into the Dark Delivered!
